0:00:00.000,0:00:04.240
Chiremba akanditaurira kuti vachadambura ruoko rwemwanakomana wangu.

0:00:04.240,0:00:06.800
Ndanga ndichirwadziwa kubva panguva iyoyo.

0:00:07.100,0:00:16.860
Ndapota cherechedza: Vhidhiyo yawave kuda kuona ndeye zvinobata mwoyo uye inoratidza maronda akazaruka kwazvo.

0:00:20.200,0:00:26.980
Izvo mwana uyu akatarisana nazvo mutoro mukuru ku mukomana muduku uyu kutakura.

0:00:26.980,0:00:31.680
Uyu mukomana muduku ane ronda paruoko pazera remakore mana.

0:00:31.680,0:00:36.680
Pazera iri, anofanirwa kunge ari kutamba akasununguka, achimhanya pamadiro, achifarira upenyu.

0:00:36.680,0:00:41.540
Asi angagotamba sei ne shamwari dzake nedambudziko rakadai seiri.

0:00:41.540,0:00:45.400
Sezvauri kuona, zvirwere zvasatani imbavha dzemufaro.

0:00:45.400,0:00:47.140
Ngatinzwei kubva kuna baba vake.

0:00:47.140,0:00:51.100
Zita rangu ndi Adegoke Ogunade. Ndine makore 36.

0:00:51.100,0:00:55.960
Tirikuona mukomana akagara pamakumbo enyu. Ndiani iye kwamuri?

0:00:55.960,0:00:57.220
Mwanakomana wangu.

0:00:57.220,0:00:59.240
Mungatiudza here zita rake nezera rake.

0:00:59.240,0:01:03.880
Zita rake ndi Favour Oluwatobi Ogunade. Ane makore mana.

0:01:03.880,0:01:07.500
Idambudziko rei raunza mwanakomana wenyu pa SCOAN nhasi?

0:01:07.500,0:01:09.940
Dambudziko ndere ronda pa ruoko.

0:01:09.940,0:01:12.860
Munoreva kuti mwanakomana wenyu ane chinetso cheronda pa ruoko?

0:01:12.860,0:01:13.900
Hongu.

0:01:13.900,0:01:16.840
Dambudziko iri reronda paruoko rakakanganisa mwanakomana wenyu sei?

0:01:16.840,0:01:19.440
Anga achinzwa sei nedambudziko iri?

0:01:19.440,0:01:23.640
Anga asinganzwe zvakanaka. Haagoni kurara.

0:01:23.640,0:01:33.000
Takapedza mari yakawanda, tichibva kuchipatara chimwe tichienda kune chimwe tichirapwa zvakasiyana siyana.

0:01:33.000,0:01:37.200
Asi zvakadaro, kwakanga kusina rubatsiro.

0:01:37.220,0:01:39.920
Ndiani akakuudzai pamusoro pezve SCOAN?

0:01:39.920,0:01:43.920
Mumwe wehanzvadzi dzangu akandiudza kuti ndiuye pano nhasi, uye

0:01:43.920,0:01:47.180
tinovimba kuti Mwari achapindura munyengetero wedu ne kumuporesa.

0:01:47.180,0:01:52.380
Munonzwa sei sababa muchiona mwanakomana wenyu ari mumamiriro ezvinhu , neurwere hwakadai?

0:01:52.380,0:01:58.980
Handisi kufara zvachose. Ini handifare pandinoona ruoko rwake.

0:01:58.980,0:02:06.040
Zvino sezvo mave pano ne mwanakomana wenyu pa SCOAN, chii chamunotenda kuti Mwari Wamasimba Ose achamuitira?

0:02:06.040,0:02:10.460
Ndinotenda kuti Mwari vachamuporesa - kuporesa zvachose nekumudzikinura.

0:02:10.460,0:02:14.100
Ameni. Tinonamata nemwi kuti Mwari Wamasimba Ose achaporesa mwanakomana wenyu ne

0:02:14.100,0:02:19.000
kumusunungura kubva pakurwara uku kwechironda cheruoko, muzita ra Jesu.

0:02:19.000,0:02:20.080
Ameni.

0:02:21.640,0:02:27.600
Mukomana uyu anongova maminitsi kubva pane chishamiso chake nokuti Jesu Kristu anongova nguva pfupi kusvika.

0:02:28.660,0:02:32.680
Kutenda isimba rinokurudzira mazwi ako kuti ashande.

0:02:32.680,0:02:36.480
Apo mu Porofita T.B. Joshua ari kunyengetera, anotaura shoko rekutenda

0:02:36.480,0:02:42.380
kune dhunamutuna rese, Jeriko rose, dambudziko rose muupenyu hwevanhu ava.

0:02:42.380,0:02:47.240
Varikubviswa kunze kwezvinetso zvavo, uye havazodzokeri shure.

0:02:47.240,0:02:50.680
Mwari ari kugadzira nzira apo panoratidza sepasina nzira.

0:02:50.680,0:02:54.800
Sezva Akaitira Mozisi, apo Akaparadzanisa Gungwa Dzvuku.

0:02:54.800,0:02:58.920
Rusvingo rumwe ne rumwe rwuri kuputswa. Dhunamutuna rese riri kuparadzwa.

0:02:58.920,0:03:02.480
Nheyo dzezvinetso zvose iri kuzunguzwa.

0:03:09.880,0:03:11.080
Tarisa pasikirini yako.

0:03:11.080,0:03:15.800
Muzita rakasimba ra Jesu Kristu.

0:03:15.800,0:03:18.880
Sununguka!

0:03:18.880,0:03:28.620
Ngationei kuti Mwari anoshandisa sei mu Porofita T.B. Joshua kuraira dambudziko romukomana uyu kuti riende, muzita ra Jesu.

0:03:28.620,0:03:30.640
Sununguka!

0:03:30.640,0:03:32.440
Muzita ra Jesu!

0:03:36.160,0:03:44.020
NGUVA YE UCHAPUPU

0:03:44.400,0:03:47.020
Zita rangu ndi Adegoke Ogunade.

0:03:47.020,0:03:50.800
Zita remwanakomana wangu Ndi Favour Ogunade.

0:03:50.800,0:03:53.220
Akanga ane dambudziko reronda paruoko.

0:03:53.220,0:03:56.680
Ndakaenda kune nzvimbo zhinji ndichitsvaga mhinduro ne chipatarawo.

0:03:56.680,0:04:02.260
Umwe we varamu vangu akandiratidza mauyiro epano.

0:04:02.260,0:04:08.460
Zuva randakauya pano, takaiswa panzvimbo ye avo vaifanirwa kuonekwa zve chimbichimbi pachechi.

0:04:08.460,0:04:11.880
Munhu wa Mwari, mu Porofita T.B. Joshua, akatinyengeterera zuva iroro,

0:04:11.880,0:04:14.600
uye kubva musi iwoyo takaona musiyano.

0:04:14.600,0:04:18.600
Vanachiremba vakanditaurira kuti vaizofanira kugura ruoko rwemwanakomana wangu.

0:04:18.600,0:04:21.380
Ndanga ndichirwadziwa kubva panguva iyoyo.

0:04:21.380,0:04:30.400
Asi nhasi, ndinotenda Mwari kuti ndine mufaro mukupupurira kuti mwanakomana wangu apora zvino.

0:04:30.400,0:04:37.820
Kare, aive nemarwadzo makuru uye ainetseka kwazvo kupfeka zvipfeko.

0:04:37.820,0:04:43.960
Ndinotenda Mwari kuti nhasi, hapasisina chironda, hapasisina marwadzo uye hapasisina kuchema.

0:04:43.960,0:04:50.380
Iye zvino, anogona kushandisa ruoko rwake, kutamba neshamwari dzake uye kuenda kuchikoro.

0:04:50.380,0:04:53.100
Ndinopa mbiri kuna Mwari Wemasimbaose!

0:04:53.100,0:04:56.180
Kuna Mwari ngakuve nekubwinya. Kubatsira avo vari kukuteererai,

0:04:56.180,0:05:04.840
mungatiudze here kuti ndezvipi zvinhu izvo mwanakomana wenyu aisagona kuita ipapo, nekuda kwechinetso chake chechironda paruoko?

0:05:04.840,0:05:10.480
Kare, akanga asingakwanise kutamba; husiku akanga asingagone kurara.

0:05:10.480,0:05:12.940
Husiku, aizochema achirwadziwa.

0:05:12.940,0:05:15.300
Iye zvino zvakanaka!

0:05:15.300,0:05:19.080
Iye zvino anogona kuenda kuchikoro ne kutamba bhora neshamwari dzake.

0:05:19.080,0:05:23.020
Iye zvino anogona kushandisa ruoko rwake kudya, kunyora ne kutamba.

0:05:23.020,0:05:25.420
Ndinopa mbiri kuna Mwari Wemasimbaose.

0:05:25.420,0:05:28.660
Tinotenda Mwari Wemasimbaose pane izvo Tenzi akaita muupenyu hwe mwanakomana wenyu.

0:05:28.660,0:05:30.700
Kubatsira avo varikukuteererai,

0:05:30.700,0:05:35.900
mungatiradze here nzvimbo iyo mwanakomana wenyu aiva nechinetso ichocho chechironda paruoko.

0:05:35.900,0:05:38.280
Maigona here kumurova rova sezvizvi kare?

0:05:38.280,0:05:39.960
Kwete, handaikwanisa kuzviedza.

0:05:39.960,0:05:40.980
Sei?

0:05:40.980,0:05:42.720
Chaive chironda chihombe.

0:05:42.720,0:05:48.980
Aigara achirwadziwa nguva dzose ne kuchema, zuva rose.

0:05:48.980,0:05:52.560
Asi kubvira pamakamuunza, uye munhu akazodzwa wa Mwari akamunamatira,

0:05:52.560,0:05:59.040
uye Mwari Wamasimba Ose akamusunungura zvachose, iye ave akasununguka zvirokwazvo kubva ku dambudziko racho. Handizvo here?

0:05:59.040,0:06:00.060
Hongu

0:06:00.060,0:06:05.300
Tinotenda Mwari. Zvino sezvo Ishe vaporesa mwanakomana wenyu uye vakakusunungurai kubva ku dambudziko iroro,

0:06:05.300,0:06:11.280
marwadzo ekumuendesa kunzvimbo muchitsvaga rubatsiro, chivimbiso chenyu kuna Mwari ndechei?

0:06:11.280,0:06:14.580
Chivimbiso changu kuna Mwari ndechekudzidzisa mwana wangu munzira ya Ishe

0:06:14.580,0:06:20.260
uye ini pachangu ndichashumira Mwari Wemasimba Ose uye nekurega kutadza zvakare.

0:06:20.260,0:06:24.280
Tinonamata pamwe nemi kuti Tenzi vachakupai nyasha dzekuzviona iwe somubatsiri

0:06:24.280,0:06:27.220
ne kudzidzisa mwana wenyu munzira yaShe.

0:06:30.900,0:06:37.900
Kare na Zvino

0:06:37.900,0:06:39.800
Kuna Mwari ngakuve kubwinya!

0:06:39.800,0:06:42.620
Dambudziko rake rave chinhu chekare.

0:06:42.620,0:06:45.440
Kusuruvara kwake kwashandurwa kuva mufaro.

0:06:45.440,0:06:47.960
Ndinokutendai, Jesu!

0:06:47.960,0:06:54.000
Tinovimba kuti wakurudzirwa nevhidhiyo yawabva mukuona.

0:06:54.000,0:07:00.360
Dzvanya apa kuti unyorese kupupurira zvakawanda pamusoro pesimba ra Mwari pabasa munguva yatiri nhasi

0:07:00.360,0:07:04.660
kuti ugare uri pamusoro pezvichagoburwa zvehuporofita, dzikinuro,

0:07:04.660,0:07:09.600
mharidzo nezvapupu zvinobva ku Synagogue Church Of All Nations

